{"tid":52363,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人認同忍屎應該加入做極限運動","createTime":"2016-12-24T04:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T02:34:49.000Z","uid":45138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"85d97b28f46a6e598a295e02e0079c029a7ff6be","tid":52363,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"極限運動（英語：Extreme Sports或XSports），泛指各種危險性較高、技巧與體能需求較高的運動項目。<br />\n<br />\n-轉自維基百科<br />\n<br />\n理據：<br />\n<br />\n1. 忍屎講求括約肌既耐力，全身既力量集中係屎眼一點同屎抗衡，鬥耐力上既性質與其他極限運動相似<br />\n<br />\n2. 技巧方面，長期忍屎可能會導致括約肌抽筋引致賴屎，識得點樣隨著便意侵襲而收放自如，收緊放鬆屎眼，技術上要求高。再者心理層面上如果稍微鬆懈，唔係專注係對抗屎上面既話隨時賴屎<br />\n<br />\n3. 危險性高我諗唔使多講，賴屎呢家野係人生最大既恥辱呢點無庸置疑<br />\n<br />\n可行性：<br />\n<br />\n1. 人人都要柯屎，人人都可以忍屎，橫跨所有年齡層，男女老幼都可以參加<br />\n<br />\n2. 器材都唔需要，只需要一個可以控制鬆緊既屎眼（有需要可以自備尿片）<br />\n<br />\n比賽種類：<br />\n<br />\n暫時構思到四人時間累積賽同埋個人技術挑戰賽<br />\n<br />\n四人時間累積賽就係搵四條友一齊忍屎，鬥長時間，拎四個人既平均時間黎鬥<br />\n<br />\n個人技術挑戰賽：按大會要求食唔同種類會導致急屎既食物，由會柯一級警棍屎至到十級肚痛計算技術分，參賽者可以忍屎其間做出唔同既體操動作增加bonus分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎指教討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa21e25795a12d9089ee035ffbceca4f80d06c8","tid":52363,"uid":648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"除左肚痛 普通急屎通常忍忍下會冇左便意🤔"},{"pid":"0cfab0f96ce229e0e817dc15004173957ac895b7","tid":52363,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4325O3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4325O3.jpg&h=3e5b0b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太陽神誕快樂<img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/BrainMonster/55.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FBrainMonster%2F55.gif&h=7563a762&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/BrainMonster/55.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FBrainMonster%2F55.gif&h=7563a762&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/BrainMonster/55.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FBrainMonster%2F55.gif&h=7563a762&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d90f0be59fc995a20c32b7551f618b7281e176a","tid":52363,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"咁我一定係最top嗰批<br />\n利申：最癲試過忍足48日"},{"pid":"6bec49fab4206c65b1cdcac2957ccc2b76d3cea0","tid":52363,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左肚痛 普通急屎通常忍忍下會冇左便意🤔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪所謂宿便？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7bc2ed0599adfe48ebd355fcbd83515348be56","tid":52363,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁我一定係最top嗰批<br />\n利申：最癲試過忍足48日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打可唔可以搵你組隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b21971723169f960eff682b8a6dbbcf0cf793fa","tid":52363,"uid":18791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁我一定係最top嗰批<br />\n利申：最癲試過忍足48日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打可唔可以搵你組隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 柯唔出同忍有分別<br />\n<br />\n願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd94b6f3cb0b34fe9b7ab84c0c99c3bf9e51de3","tid":52363,"uid":188279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"上次急到跪左係到唔敢行，一放鬆真係會爆，好彩返到屋企"}]}